(3170, 1, '2015-02-10 23:03:19', '2015-02-10 23:03:19', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]NHK uses cookies to deliver superior functionality and to enhance your experience of our websites. Continued use of this site indicates that you accept this policy.\n\nCookies are small text files stored on your computer by your browser. They''re used for many things, such as remembering whether you''ve visited the site before, so that you remain logged in - or to help us work out how many new website visitors we get each month. They contain information about the use of your computer but don''t include personal information about you (they don''t store your name, for instance).\n\nThis policy explains how cookies are used on NHK websites in general - and, below, how you can control the cookies that may be used on this site (not all of them are used on every site).\n\n<strong>About this Cookie policy </strong>\n\nThis Cookie Policy applies to all of our websites and our mobile applications ("the Website"). In this Cookie Policy, when we refer to any of our Websites, we mean any website or mobile application operated by or on behalf of Glenmere Technology Ltd or its subsidiaries and affiliates, regardless of how you access the network. By accessing the Website, you agree that this Cookie Policy will apply whenever you access the Website on any device. Any changes to this policy will be posted here. We reserve the right to vary this Cookie Policy from time to time and such changes shall become effective as soon as they are posted. Your continued use of the Website constitutes your agreement to all such changes.\n\n<strong>Our use of cookies </strong>\n\nWe may collect information automatically when you visit the Website, using cookies. The cookies allow us to identify your computer and find out details about your last visit. You can choose, below, not to allow cookies. If you do, we can''t guarantee that your experience with the Website will be as good as if you do allow cookies. The information collected by cookies does not personally identify you; it includes general information about your computer settings, your connection to the Internet e.g. operating system and platform, IP address, your browsing patterns and timings of browsing on the Website and your location. Most internet browsers accept cookies automatically, but you can change the settings of your browser to erase cookies or prevent automatic acceptance if you prefer.\n\n<strong>Types of cookie that may be used during your visit to the Website: </strong>\n\nThe following types of cookie are used on this site. We don''t list every single cookie used by name - but for each type of cookie we tell you how you can control its use.\n\n<strong>1. Personalisation cookies </strong>\n\nThese cookies are used to recognise repeat visitors to the Website and in conjunction with other information we hold to attempt to record specific browsing information (that is, about the way you arrive at the Website, pages you view, options you select, information you enter and the path you take through the Website). These are used to recommend content we think you''ll be interested in based on what you''re looked at before.\n\n<strong>2. Analytics cookies </strong>\n\nThese monitor how visitors move around the Website and how they reached it. This is used so that we can see total (not individual) figures on which types of content users enjoy most.\n\n<strong>3. Third-party service cookies </strong>\n\nSocial sharing, video and other services we offer are run by other companies. These companies may drop cookies on your computer when you use them on our site or if you are already logged in to them.\n\n<strong>4. Site management cookies </strong>\n\nThese are used to maintain your identity or session on the Website. For instance, where our websites run on more than one server, we use a cookie to ensure that you are sent information by one specific server (otherwise you may log in or out unexpectedly). We may use similar cookies when you vote in opinion polls to ensure that you can only vote once, and to ensure that you can use our commenting functionality when not logged in (to ensure you don''t see comments you''ve reported as abusive, for instance, or don''t vote comments up/down more than once).\n\nThese cookies cannot be turned off individually but you could change your browser setting to refuse all cookies (see above) if you do not wish to accept them.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Cookie Policy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cookie-policy', '', '', '2015-02-10 23:03:19', '2015-02-10 23:03:19', '', 0, 'http://www.nhkeu.co.uk/?page_id=3170', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3233, 1, '2015-03-15 13:58:53', '2015-03-15 13:58:53', '<strong>各位在英华人消费者/网民：</strong>\n\n2015年3月14号晚，在微信朋友圈中发生了针对“拿回扣”购物ＡＰＰ的恶意谣言事件，严重损害了英国华人消费者的正当权益。为维护广大在英华人消费者权益和网民的知情权，针对此事件本公司现发表以下正式声明：\n\nGlenmere Technology Ltd 是一家注册在英国的移动互联网公司，旗下的“<strong>拿回扣”购物ＡＰＰ是一款专注于英国华人奢侈品线下购物返利的手机软件</strong>，于２０１５年２月２８号正式上线。<strong>软件旨在为在英工作，学习，生活的华人朋友提供更多高端购物的返利优惠。</strong>软件上线两周内，得到了广大消费者的热烈欢迎，软件的注册量和使用量节节攀升。\n\n在２０１５年３月１４号晚，微信朋友圈中开始出现针对<strong>“拿回扣”ＡＰＰ的恶意诽谤，谣言散布者恶意中伤软件</strong>，发布诸如“有不法之徒在网上发布的拿回扣ＡＰＰ带有病毒，不要打开，立刻删除”等文字，还谎称“新闻中已经播放该消息”等虚假信息，鼓动不知情的网民进行转发，此事件对于本公司，软件用户以及广大在英华人消费者造成了极其恶劣的传播影响。\n\n据调查，<strong>该事件系某些个人和小团体担心“拿回扣”ＡＰＰ向广大消费者提供返利优惠后，影响了这部分人的既得利益，而动用非法手段</strong>，捏造虚假信息利用微信平台进行传播。本公司法务部门将动用法律手段向谣言始作俑者发送律师信，追究其法律责任，维护软件用户的合法权益。\n\n<strong>在此，敬告各位网民，在不知情的情况下，不要轻易转发传播此类谣言，以免由于传播范围的扩大导致巨大的社会危害，导致您个人被追究连带的法律责任。</strong>\n\n就谣言中所涉及的软件的一些列安全性问题，本公司作出以下回复：\n\n１.　关于软件安全问题，本公司的“拿回扣”ＡＰＰ经过一年的开发，投资超过上百万人民币，是经过苹果商店和Google Play审核认证，并在其网上商店发布供网民免费下载的返利软件。<strong>所有经过苹果公司和谷歌公司审核并发布的软件在安全性上都不存在任何问题</strong>，否则苹果公司或谷歌公司也将要承担相关法律责任。请各位消费者放心下载和使用。\n\n２.　关于信息安全问题，由于软件的功能中涉及消费后返利的功能，的确需要消费者提供个人账户信息，但本公司有着一套完善的个人信息保护系统，保证用户的信息安全，不会泄露给第三方。<strong>本</strong><strong>公司是英国信息管理局ICO的注册单位，拥有该监管部门发放的Data Protection注册牌照，注册号：No.ZA104520，</strong>可以通过ＩＣＯ官网进行查询：www.ico.org.uk\n\n3. 关于支付安全问题，消费者通过软件进入商店后，直接向商家进行购物支付。本软件只提供返利信息和返利记录，<strong>并不参与支付过程，根本不涉及任何银行卡交易</strong>，自然不存在任何支付安全的问题！\n\n特别提醒各位网民，<strong>不法分子无处不在</strong>，在网上要做好相关的信息辨识工作，以免在无意识的情况下，被不法分子利用，而承担相应法律责任！\n\n<strong>在此要感谢广大消费者和网民对于“拿回扣”APP和本公司一如既往的支持和信赖，我们将会为大家提供更好的服务以及更多的优惠购物体验！</strong>\n\nGlenmere Technology Ltd\n\n2015年3月15号', '致全英国华人消费者公告 务必阅读！转发告知周围朋友！', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', '%e8%87%b4%e5%85%a8%e8%8b%b1%e5%9b%bd%e5%8d%8e%e4%ba%ba%e6%b6%88%e8%b4%b9%e8%80%85%e5%85%ac%e5%91%8a-%e5%8a%a1%e5%bf%85%e9%98%85%e8%af%bb%ef%bc%81%e8%bd%ac%e5%8f%91%e5%91%8a%e7%9f%a5%e5%91%a8%e5%9b%b4', '', '', '2015-03-15 13:58:53', '2015-03-15 13:58:53', '', 0, 'http://www.nhkeu.co.uk/?p=3233', 0, 'post', '', 0),
