(3268, 1, '2015-04-04 21:28:29', '2015-04-04 21:28:29', '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1417280292623{margin-bottom: -10px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-image: url(http://localhost:81/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/oxford-street-shopping-spree-pic-getty-images-54290565_PS11.jpg?id=2918) !important;background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}" ia_row_style="0" ia_row_paralax="1" ia_row_scheme="1"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="152px"][ia_heading size="1" align="center"]NHK member portal[/ia_heading][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1423137043001{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">NHK provides you exclusive access to rewards from all your favourite brands wherever you shop.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>SHOP</strong> around using NHK app; get <strong>NAVIGATED</strong> to the retailer by the app;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">get your QR code <strong>SCANNED</strong>; <strong>SNAP</strong> and <strong>UPLOAD</strong> the receipt,</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>T</strong><strong>RACK</strong> your footprint and receive <strong>CASHBACK</strong> securely into your bank or PayPal account - it''s easy!</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][ias_showcase showcase="2105"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1412701079492{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}" ia_row_style="0" ia_row_paralax="0" ia_row_scheme="0"][vc_column width="1/2"][ia_heading size="0" align="left"]Connect with us[/ia_heading][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2688" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182872742{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2692" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182877711{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2907" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1428182882545{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2689" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182887089{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2694" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1428182892894{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2693" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182897530{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2691" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182902690{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2690" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182907752{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text][mc4wp_form][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][ia_heading size="0" align="left"]WHAT CAN WE DO FOR NHK MEMBERS[/ia_heading][vc_accordion][vc_accordion_tab title="BRING YOU TO THE RETAILER’S DOORSTEP"][vc_column_text]The unique “Cashback Radar” feature will enable you to find the nearest retailer with cashback rewards and NHK will navigate you to the retailer’s doorstep.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="YOU CAN TRACK THE WHOLE CASHBACK PROGRESS"][vc_column_text]Every step of the Cashback experience can be tracked clearly through the “My Footprint” feature, so you know exactly when you will be rewarded.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="REWARDS ARE BETTER THAN ANYTHING"][vc_column_text]NHK app takes the commission (termed "cashback") usually paid by retailers to third-party referrers and passes it on to NHK members. You can even choose your own currency![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Reward Members', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2951-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-04 21:28:29', '2015-04-04 21:28:29', '', 2951, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/?p=3268', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3269, 1, '2015-04-04 21:29:28', '2015-04-04 21:29:28', '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1417282466930{background-color: #ffffff !important;}" ia_row_style="0" ia_row_paralax="0" ia_row_scheme="0"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="152px"][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1417282934995{margin-bottom: -102px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1417283949237{padding-top: 32px !important;}"][ia_heading size="1" align="center"]NHK retailer portal[/ia_heading][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">NHK is a game-changing app that enables luxury brands to connect directly with NHK members before, during and after their shopping experience via 6 unique steps:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>SCAN – CHECK – CONFIRM – TRACK – SUMMARIZE – ANALYSE</strong></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[ia_button id="button_8" size="big" solid="0" link="http://www.nhkeu.co.uk/partnership-enquiries" icon="fa-question-circle" arrow="0" color="#" css_animation="" animation_delay=""]Partnership Enquiries[/ia_button] [ia_button id="button_8" size="big" solid="0" link="http://www.nhkeu.co.uk/partnership-enquiries" icon="fa-sign-in" arrow="0" color="#" css_animation="" animation_delay=""]Log In[/ia_button]</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1417282667642{padding-bottom: -50px !important;}"][ias_showcase showcase="1861"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row ia_row_style="0" ia_row_paralax="0" ia_row_scheme="0"][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1417281749549{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][ia_iconbox icon="fa-qrcode" heading="Scan" layout="left"]<strong>SCAN</strong> a customer’s QR code[/ia_iconbox][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1417281771977{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][ia_iconbox icon="fa-check-square-o " heading="Check" layout="left"]<strong>CHECK</strong> if the receipt uploaded by the a customer is genuine[/ia_iconbox][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1417281778627{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][ia_iconbox icon="fa-gavel" heading="Confirm" layout="left"]<strong>CONFIRM</strong> a cash back request[/ia_iconbox][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row ia_row_style="0" ia_row_paralax="0" ia_row_scheme="0"][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1417281870911{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][ia_iconbox icon="fa-eye" heading="Track" layout="left"]<strong>TRACK</strong> the cash backs progress[/ia_iconbox][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1417281878474{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][ia_iconbox icon="fa-usd " heading="Summarize" layout="left"]<strong>SUMMARIZE</strong> the cash back amount[/ia_iconbox][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1417281900390{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][ia_iconbox icon="fa-bar-chart " heading="Analyze" layout="left"]<strong>ANALYZE</strong> consumers behaviour[/ia_iconbox][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1421882639281{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #fcfcfc !important;}" ia_row_style="0" ia_row_paralax="0" ia_row_scheme="0"][vc_column width="1/1" css=".vc_custom_1421882860349{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][ia_heading size="0" align="left"]Retailer Portal[/ia_heading][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[ia_button id="button_9" size="big" solid="0" link="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&amp;url=https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/nhkapps/iosapp/NHKshop.plist" icon="fa-apple" arrow="0" color="#" css_animation="" animation_delay=""]       Retailer IOS        [/ia_button]</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[ia_button id="button_8" size="big" solid="1" link="http://www.nhkeu.co.uk/download/retailer.apk" icon="fa-android" arrow="0" color="#" css_animation="" animation_delay=""]   Retailer Android     [/ia_button]</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1417282482941{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}" ia_row_style="0" ia_row_paralax="0" ia_row_scheme="0"][vc_column width="1/2"][ia_heading size="0" align="left"]Connect with us[/ia_heading][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2688" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182932657{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2692" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182937288{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2907" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1428182941790{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2689" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182946861{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2694" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1428182952701{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2693" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182957995{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2691" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182962655{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][vc_single_image image="2690" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" css=".vc_custom_1428182967216{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text][mc4wp_form][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][ia_heading size="0" align="left"]What Can We Do for NHK Retailers[/ia_heading][vc_accordion][vc_accordion_tab title="MORE EFFECTIVE MARKETING INVESTMENT"][vc_column_text]Your marketing investment is more effective because the rewards are delivered directly to the shopper, driving the behaviour and developing the personal relationship you want to create with your consumers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="SECTOR EXPERTISE"][vc_column_text]Our team members are all Luxury Industry marketing, sales and category experts. We understand how to create a customised programme of activity that helps luxury brands connect directly with their consumers and building long-term brand loyalty in a 21st century way.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="NO MORE PAPER COUPONS"][vc_column_text]With our digital solution, there is none of the hassle and slowness of paper coupons. Smart millennial shoppers don’t want to print out pieces of paper at home; instead they expect their interactions to be personalised, fast and digital. That''s NHK![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Help Retailers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2947-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-04 21:29:28', '2015-04-04 21:29:28', '', 2947, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress/?p=3269', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
